content.rendered:
Directed by Harish Shankar

Written by Madhu Srinivas. Mithun Chaitanya. Harish Shankar. Harish Shankar. Madhu Srinivas. Mithun Chaitanya. Rishabh Purohit

Cast Varun Tej (Gaddalakonda Ganesh). Atharvaa Murali (Abhilash). Mirnalini Ravi (Bujjamma). Pooja Hegde (Sridevi) .Ananth. Annapoorna (Ganesh’s chef). Darbha Appaji Ambarisha (Sridevi Father). Raghu Babu (Film director). Tanikella Bharani (Chalam). Brahmaji (Muni Manikyam). Brahmanandam (Brahmanandam). Krishna Manjusha c (Film Heroine (as Manjusha Chivukula Krishna)).Vamsee Chaganti. Dimple Hayathi (Item number).Prasanna Kumar.Gururaj Manepalli. Bhaskar Manyam ((as Bhaskar)).Nagineedu. Vinay Nallakadi (NA (archive footage)). Nithiin (Nithiin). Supriya Pathak (Ganesh’s mother). Pradeep (Abhi’s father). Raja Ravindra (Nallamandu Babji).Ramana Reddy. Satya (Kondamalli). Shatru (Kasi). Prabhas Sreenu (Balija). Subbaraju (Prabhakar’s henchman). Sukumar (Sukumar). Manikanta Varanasi (Sales Executive). Fish Venkat (Khanberi Kantayya). Yarlee (Gani follower)

Languages Telugu

Producers Gopichand Achanta. Ram Achanta. Harish Katta

Production 14 Reels Plu. Goldmines Telefilm
